Set less than 0.6 mi from Meir Park, Brown Lighthouse Tel Aviv, a member of Brown Hotels in Tel Aviv offers free bikes. The property is around a 12-minute walk from Dizengoff Center and 0.7 mi from Dizengoff Square. The property is 1.2 mi from Shenkin Street. All guest rooms in the hotel are equipped with a flat-screen TV with satellite channels. Every room is equipped with a private bathroom, while some feature a sea view. The rooms at Brown Lighthouse Tel Aviv, a member of Brown Hotels come with a seating area. A buffet breakfast can be enjoyed at the property. Guests can enjoy a meal at the in-house restaurant, which specializes in International cuisine and also offers gluten-free options. Cycling is among the activities that guests can enjoy near the accommodations. Speaking Arabic, English and French at the 24-hour front desk, staff are always at hand to help. Gordon Swimming Pool is 1.3 mi from the hotel, while Itzhak Rabin Memorial is 1.4 mi away. The nearest airport is Ben Gurion Airport, 15 mi from Brown Lighthouse Tel Aviv, a member of Brown Hotels. Due to ongoing roadworks, guests are advised to access the hotel at 8 Idelson by car or taxi.This is a temporary situation caused by the roadworks.
